---
// About Us page for COPAK GENERAL TRADING
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<title>About Us | COPAK GENERAL TRADING</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Learn more about COPAK GENERAL TRADING, our mission, vision, and values." />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<header>
			<img src="/favicon.png" alt="COPAK Logo" style="height:60px; margin:1rem 0;" />
			<h1>About Us</h1>
			<nav>
				<a href="/">Home</a> |
				<a href="/about">About Us</a> |
				<a href="/services">Services</a> |
				<a href="/our-strength">Our Strength</a> |
				<a href="/contact">Contact</a>
			</nav>
		</header>
		<main>
			<section>
				<h2>Our Company</h2>
				<p>COPAK GENERAL TRADING (CGT) supports procurement, engineering, and maintenance teams with practical industrial solutions, from sourcing critical components to delivering specialized field services.</p>
				<h3>Vision</h3>
				<p>To become a leading industrial solutions company in the Democratic Republic of Congo.</p>
				<h3>Mission</h3>
				<p>Deliver reliable, innovative, and adaptive services that improve safety, uptime, and performance for industrial clients.</p>
				<h3>Core Values</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Excellence</li>
					<li>Innovation</li>
					<li>Adaptability</li>
					<li>Commitment</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
	<head>
		<title>About Us | COPAK GENERAL TRADING</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Learn more about COPAK GENERAL TRADING, our mission, vision, and values." />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />
		<style>
			.hero-overlay {
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(26, 58, 42, 0.9) 0%, rgba(26, 58, 42, 0.5) 100%);
			}
			.hero-content {
				position: relative;
				z-index: 2;
				padding: 5rem 0;
				max-width: 640px;
				color: #fff;
			}
			.hero-eyebrow {
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.15em;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
				margin: 0 0 1rem;
			}
			.hero-content h1 {
				font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				color: #fff;
			}
			.hero-sub {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				line-height: 1.7;
				color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
				margin: 0;
			}
			.content-section {
				padding: 5rem 0;
			}
			.two-col {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
				gap: 4rem;
				align-items: center;
			}
			.col-text h2 {
				font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
				margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
			}
			.col-text p {
				color: var(--text-light);
				line-height: 1.75;
				margin: 0 0 1rem;
			}
			.col-image {
				border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
				overflow: hidden;
				box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
			}
			.col-image img {
				display: block;
				width: 100%;
				height: 380px;
				object-fit: cover;
			}
			.values-section {
				padding: 5rem 0;
				background: var(--surface);
			}
			.values-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}
			.value-card {
				padding: 2rem;
				border: 1px solid var(--border);
				border-radius: var(--radius-md);
				transition: all 0.25s ease;
			}
			.value-card:hover {
				box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
				transform: translateY(-2px);
			}
			.value-card h3 {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
				color: var(--primary);
			}
			.value-card p {
				color: var(--text-light);
				line-height: 1.65;
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 0.95rem;
			}
			.process-section {
				padding: 5rem 0;
			}
			.process-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}
			.process-card {
				padding: 2rem;
				background: var(--surface);
				border: 1px solid var(--border);
				border-radius: var(--radius-md);
			}
			.process-num {
				display: inline-block;
				font-weight: 700;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				color: var(--primary-light);
				letter-spacing: 0.08em;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}
			.process-card h3 {
				font-size: 1.3rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
			}
			.process-card p {
				color: var(--text-light);
				line-height: 1.65;
				margin: 0;
			}
			.team-section {
				padding: 5rem 0;
				background: var(--surface);
			}
			.team-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}
			.team-card {
				text-align: center;
				padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
				border: 1px solid var(--border);
				border-radius: var(--radius-md);
			}
			.team-avatar {
				width: 4rem;
				height: 4rem;
				margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
				border-radius: 50%;
				background: var(--primary);
				color: #fff;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				font-weight: 700;
				font-size: 1.1rem;
			}
			.team-card h3 {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
			}
			.team-role {
				display: block;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				color: var(--primary-light);
				font-weight: 500;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}
			.team-card p {
				color: var(--text-light);
				line-height: 1.65;
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				margin: 0;
			}
			.photos-section {
				padding: 5rem 0;
			}
			.photos-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
				gap: 1rem;
			}
			.photo-card {
				margin: 0;
				position: relative;
				border-radius: var(--radius-md);
				overflow: hidden;
			}
			.photo-card img {
				display: block;
				width: 100%;
				height: 260px;
				object-fit: cover;
				transition: transform 0.4s ease;
			}
			.photo-card:hover img {
				transform: scale(1.05);
			}
			.photo-card figcaption {
				position: absolute;
				bottom: 0;
				left: 0;
				right: 0;
				padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 1.25rem;
				background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7));
				color: #fff;
				opacity: 0;
				transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
			}
			.photo-card:hover figcaption {
				opacity: 1;
			}
			.photo-card figcaption strong {
				display: block;
				margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
			}
			.photo-card figcaption span {
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
			}
			@media (max-width: 960px) {
				.two-col,
				.values-grid,
				.process-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
				}
				.team-grid,
				.photos-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
			}
			@media (max-width: 640px) {
				.two-col,
				.values-grid,
				.process-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
				.page-hero {
					min-height: 40vh;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>